          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "d0d510a4",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "As we navigate the challenges of the Coronavirus (COVID-19) pandemic, declared a global health crisis by the World Health Organization, businesses both large and small face unprecedented challenges. The shift in consumer behavior, marked by decreased outings and a reliance on alternative shopping methods, has impacted local and global economies. With quarantine measures and the consequent loss of wages, our focus turns towards steps that can safely reignite necessary commercial activities.\n\nThe CDC (Centers for Disease Control and Prevention) emphasizes the importance of minimizing exposure as a key preventive measure. This involves practicing social distancing, wearing appropriate PPE, and maintaining good hygiene, especially through thorough hand washing.\n\nDuring these trying times, Midland Floor Care is committed to supporting healthcare facilities, grocery store chains, and other retail clients of varying sizes. By rigorously adhering to CDC guidelines for cleaning and disinfecting, and utilizing EPA-registered chemicals, we offer top-tier cleaning, disinfection, and surface protection services.\n\nWe are here to assist in this period of recovery. If you need our services, please don't hesitate to reach out. Let us know how we can help.\n\nPlease let me know if there's anything else you need or if you'd like any further modifications to this text.\n\n<a href=\"http://midlandfloors.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-we-kill-covid19.pdf.pdf\">\nDOWNLOAD \"HOW WE KILL COVID19\" CHECKLECT\n</a>\n<h2>The Midland Covid Promise</h2>\n<img src=\"http://midlandfloors.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/abou-icon2png.png\" alt=\"image\" />\n<h4>High - Touch Cleaning</h4>\nWe hereby certify that all cleaning and disinfecting procedures are performed in accordance with CDC Guidelines\n<img src=\"http://midlandfloors.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/abou-icon2png.png\" alt=\"image\" />\n<h4>Disinfectants</h4>\nALL Disinfectant Chemistry appears on the EPA Approved List of Disinfectants Effective against COVID19 (List \"N\") *The EPA List \"N\" is a directory of chemistry that is effective in killing COVID-19 specifically\n<img src=\"https://tv.fixherotheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/abou-icon2png.png\" alt=\"image\" />\n<h4>Surface Protectant</h4>\nALL Surface Protectant Chemistry prevents viruses, pathogens and bacteria from growing on treated surfaces for 90 DAYS!! Our Surface Protectant is also ACTIVELY Registered with the EPA (BioProtect 500 EPA#87583-3)\n<h2>Our Chemistry</h2>\n<h4><a href=\"https://www.legendbrandsrestoration.com/Fileshare/Documents/Products/2843/Mediclean%20Disinfectant%20Spray%20Plus%20US%20AGHS%20Published%20SDS%20March%206%202018%20LG-1041.PDF\">\nMediclean </a></h4>\nMediClean Disinfectant Spray Plus (formerly Microban)also provides long-lasting residual protection, so it keeps working, preventing germs and fungi from growing on surfaces long after application. Major insurance companies recognize MediClean Disinfectant Spray for treatment on water losses. MediClean Disinfectant Spray Plus is EPA registered for many decontamination applications, including water damage restoration, sewage backups, removal of carcasses, toilet overflow situations, and more. It is also EPA registered for both spray and cold fogging applications. EPA registration number: 70385-5 Apply to hard surfaces, carpet, upholstery, and mattresses - just about any surface in need of cleaning and disinfecting.\n<h4>BioProtect</h4>\nBio-Protect 500 creates a Micro-biostatic Antimicrobial Coating on the surface that inhibits odor causing bacteria, mold, mildew and viruses. The Micro-biostatic Antimicrobial Coating forms a protective surface protectant by forming a nano bed of spikes that disrupts the microorganism's membrane resulting in the loss of energy in the microbe and its demise. This new technology provides a perfect approach to inhibiting microorganisms without the use of unsafe heavy metals or poisons. This mode of action is entirely unique to other antimicrobials.\n\n<a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/staff-training/\">Staff Training</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/floor-care-services/\">Services</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/clients-we-serve/\">Clients We Serve</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/\">Home</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/ultimate-guide-to-floor-care-for-retail/\">Ultimate Guide to Floor Care for Retail</a>",
                "align": "left",
                "text_color": "#0F1411",
